   <h2 class="listicle-header__header listicle-header__header--center">
      
      Arsenal books – history of the club
      
      
   </h2>
</div>
<div class="basicTextBlock  fourty"><p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">The two Arsenal books in this selection&nbsp;present&nbsp;a different angle on the club&rsquo;s illustrious 147-year history: as told by The Telegraph; through the deeds of controversial figures who have influenced the club; and through the feats of its greatest goalscorers.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-12 articleList article--center article--underline">
      <div class="article__image-wrapper"><img src="//books.telegraph.co.uk/RichContent/Products/9781472632203/ProductImage/a5ec11da-772b-4b26-ab65-e0af9006fa33_medium.jpg" alt="Arsenal Football Headlines - The Telegraph Custom Gift Book"></div>
      <div class="article__content">
          <div class="article__header">
              <h3><a  href="https://books.telegraph.co.uk/Product/Arsenal-Football-Headlines---The-Telegraph-Custom-Gift-Book/27331424">Arsenal Football Headlines - The Telegraph Custom Gift Book</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="article__desc">The ultimate Arsenal book. Reproduced articles, match reports and iconic photographs from The Daily Telegraph and The Sunday Telegraph record how the papers have covered the club from 1886. With 13 league titles, a record 14 FA Cup wins and another four major trophies, Arsenal are one of the most successful teams in English football history. This personalised Telegraph Gift Book maps out their story from their formation as Dial Square to the successful eras under Herbert Chapman, George Graham and Arsène Wenger, and their move to the Emirates Stadium after 93 years at Highbury. The perfect Arsenal gift.</div>
          <div class="article__cta"><a  class="button btn" href="https://books.telegraph.co.uk/Product/Arsenal-Football-Headlines---The-Telegraph-Custom-Gift-Book/27331424">Read more</a></div>          
